<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Welcome to <%= websiteName %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #000000;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #000000;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h1 {
      color: #f5a300;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    p {
      margin: 10px 0;
      color: white !important;
    }

    .logo {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .logo img {
      width: 50px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #f5a300;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .contact-info {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .contact-info p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    .contact-info a {
      color: aqua;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="https://<%= websiteLink %>/img/maillogo.png" alt="Logo">
    </div>
    <p> Hello <%= username %> </p>
    <p>Thank you for signing up to <%= websiteName %></p>
    <p>
      Our platform helps you navigate the intricate world of investments, delving across varying financial market instruments trading with ease and confidence. 
      Whether you're a seasoned investor or just starting out, our intuitive interface, real-time data analytics, and dedicated support ensures you're always in the best position to make informed trading decisions to make the most off the market.      
    </p>
    <p>
      Dive in and let us be your trusted partner in your investment journey.
    </p>
    <p>
      For enquiries, you can always reach us via email
    </p>
    <div class="contact-info">
      <p>Website: <a href="<%= websiteLink %>"><%= websiteLink %></a></p>
      <p>Email: <a href="mailto:<%= websiteSupportMail %>"><%= websiteSupportMail %></a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>